message: Hi Bob, I'm selling a product that I believe you'll find valuable. I'm offering it to you for $115.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate your suggestion. I am willing to pay $100 for the product.
Bob, I understand your position, but I can't sell the product for less than $110. This is my final offer.
I see, Alice. I am still interested in the product, but I am only able to pay $105. Let me know if this is within your range.
